                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_8d8Pk8": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Absolutely! In fact it works better if you sweat a lot because as the CoolClip™ circulates air inside your shirt, it makes your sweat evaporate much faster, which quickly draws heat away from your skin. Therefore, even during the hottest summer days, it is still the most effective personal cooling device that keeps you cooled all day long.</p>",
